name: DON'T TREAD ON ME SO HORY!!!
description: I TOOK THIS SHOT AS I WAS OUT ON A PHOTO EXCURSION TO MOUNT TAMALPIAS IN MARIN COUNTY CA, WITH THE PROFESSIONAL PHOTOGRAPHERS OF WINE COUNTY, I FOUND THIS BEAUTIFUL PRICKLY PLANT ON THE GROUND, THEY WERE ALL OVER THE PLACE. AFTER EACH SALE THE PRICE WILL GO UP.
